[{"id":"UgxvA_OOJVlngRAO1bR4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"This wad has some good soundtrack. So far, what I've figured for other levels thanks to The Doom Wiki as well as info from the music lumps, plus some music knowledge of my own:\n\n-Map 1: Король и Шут - Воспоминания о былой любви (King and Jester - Memories of a Past Love).\n-Map 2: Mark Klem - The Everlasting Negative (Requiem map 21).\n-Map 4: unnamed MIDI by Andrew \"CoRaX\" Wood.\n-Map 5: \"Act on Instinct\" from Command & Conquer.\n-Map 6: Radiohead - Street Spirit (Fade Out).\n-Map 7: \"Missions 1 & 2\" from ALIEN³.\n-Map 8: Soulfly - Umbabaraumba.\n-Map 9: Misfits - Dig Up Her Bones.\n-Map 12: Kevin Schilder - Atcoty (Heretic maps E1M9, E3M8, and E4M9.)\n-Map 13: Carcass - Corporal Jigsore Quandary.\n-Map 21: Silent Circle - 2Night ('90s version).\n-Map 25: Rammstein - Amour.\n-Map 30 (dietest18.wad): Limp Bizkit - Eat You Alive, and Diamond Head - Helpless (the music lump credits Metallica, though).\n-Intermission music: In Flames - Worlds Within the Margin.","like_count":5,"author_id":"UCnO7D4RM1vxFa8AlM2sKCpQ","author":"@T0rturephile","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_mFhYmojQ4r8PSRyEMrF43yvQkYRKQ5rypSE7vnFFZFhE4=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@T0rturephile","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1745712000,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgxvA_OOJVlngRAO1bR4AaABAg.A3ocyLuefbhAMNdh7_Me6G","parent":"UgxvA_OOJVlngRAO1bR4AaABAg","text":"Soundtrack\n\n    MAP01: MIDI rendition of \"Vospominaniya o Byloy Lyubvi\" by Korol i Shut\n    MAP02: \"The Everlasting Negative\" by Mark Klem, from Requiem\n    MAP03:\n    MAP04: \"Untitled\" by Andrew Wood (Corax)\n    MAP05: MIDI rendition of \"Act on Instinct\" from Command & Conquer\n    MAP06: MIDI rendition of \"Street Spirit (Fade Out)\" by Radiohead\n    MAP07: MIDI rendition of \"Missions 1 & 2\" from Alien 3 (NES)\n    MAP08: MIDI rendition of \"Umbabaraumba\" by Soulfly\n    MAP09: MIDI rendition of \"Dig Up Her Bones\" by The Misfits\n    MAP10: MIDI rendition of \"Tears (Kyo Kusanagi Theme)\" from The King of Fighters '99\n    MAP11:\n    MAP12: \"Atcoty\" by Kevin Schilder, from Heretic\n    MAP13: MIDI rendition of \"Corporeal Jigsore Quandry\" by Carcass\n    MAP14: \"Give In (With Pleasure)\" by Mark Klem, from Memento Mori II\n    MAP15:\n    MAP16: MIDI rendition of \"Heartwork\" by Carcass\n    MAP17:\n    MAP18:\n    MAP19:\n    MAP20: MIDI rendition of \"Proklyatyy staryy dom\" by Korol i Shut\n    MAP21: MIDI rendition of \"2Night\" by Silent Circle\n    MAP22: no replacement\n    MAP23: no replacement\n    MAP25: MIDI rendition of \"Amour\" by Rammstein\n    MAP26: no replacement\n    MAP27: no replacement\n    MAP30: no replacement\n    MAP33: no music","like_count":1,"author_id":"UCd4ANTdP0AJ11F10NwA0OqQ","author":"@FëanorFingolfin1","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_kou3dO5GhrvBQru7jrDY7-p0Ls3-FwpdfJn_A0CdgtFmBIy5ofV2XYbnym-k-Zi8t6WA=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@F%C3%ABanorFingolfin1","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1758931200,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgwoVGmpC8_u6B4GEol4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"Kyo Tears.","like_count":4,"author_id":"UC6bCRfJf2-FbwQcaFMTIZ9w","author":"@apenasvortex6531","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ZNuAXA6BebT-9cnznjxpabX6-OL0z9SRMvyjQmSuLeqaGaoeXCapts0tSoGLVPm0I-okiLj0=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@apenasvortex6531","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1714176000,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgwhwmdZg7dGueLWiBB4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"King of Fighters 99 Tears","like_count":5,"author_id":"UCqgZokixxUx4QZ610tOEyjA","author":"@IAMNOTRANA","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_lCxKOFr_MJjADavmUcz8uAPNxvHsKm9RVvyve8hglhvVk=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@IAMNOTRANA","is_favorit